title: Dark SASI 2018 (PC-ENG)
description:
Year of release: May 19, 2018 
Genre: Action / Adventure / RPG 
Developer: Narko Games 
Publisher: Narko Games 
Platform: PC 
Publication Type: License 
Language: English 
Language: English 
Tabletka: Present (PLAZA) - Operating system: Windows / 7 / 8/10 - Processor: Quad-core Intel or AMD, 2.5 GHz or faster - RAM: 4 GB RAM - Video: NVIDIA GeForce 470 GTX or AMD Radeon 6870 HD series card or higher - DirectX version 11 - Hard disk space : 6 GB

Dark SASI is an adventure in the style of an RPG, with its own characteristics. 
Immerse yourself in the gloom and dark atmosphere of "Dark SASI". 
Any wrong move or rash act will lead to death. 
You are waiting for large and psychologically complex BOSS. 
Your soul is saved only near the "teleport souls," but there are not so many. Proceed with caution. 
You will be accompanied by more than 20 tracks, giving the opportunity to dive headlong into fear and despondency.

Installation:

1. Install the game 
2. Copy the contents of the PLAZA folder to the folder with the game installed, replace. 
3. Play
